Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.35,0:00:04.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:07.02,somari text,,0,0,0,,304年前  只有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:08.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,是个图书馆管理人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:12.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,伊索尔德·内波夫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:14.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,你说的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:15.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:17.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,是这座图书馆的馆长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:21.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是  如果是这么久远以前的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:22.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,那这个人就已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:23.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:27.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,魔女的寿命约是150年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:32.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,不过  被选拔为馆长这样优秀的魔女很长寿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:35.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,只是  馆长的身体状况…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:37.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:39.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:43.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,我说  为什么这本书这么重要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:46.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,这关系到我们旅行的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:48.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.61,0:00:51.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么了  小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:54.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:01.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:03.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,给你我珍藏的书
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:05.50,somari text,,0,0,0,,你就放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:07.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,送你个人情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:10.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,----op----
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.04,0:01:22.79,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}何なんだろう　この胸のモヤモヤは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.04,0:01:22.79,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}心中的这份躁动  是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.09,0:01:30.55,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}洗いたてのタオルに顔を埋めるような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.09,0:01:30.55,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}就像将脸埋入刚洗过的毛巾一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:37.68,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}鳥が鳴いている　朝焼けのメロディー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:37.68,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}鸟儿们吟唱着  朝霞的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:48.74,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}どこまで歩いても　この道は続いている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:48.74,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}无论走到哪  这道路都会延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:57.84,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}手を繋ぐよりも　指を繋ぐような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:57.84,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}比起手牵手  更像是紧握这手指
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:04.61,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}寒い夜は寄り添い合って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:04.61,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}寒冷的夜晚彼此相依
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:09.97,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}星空の毛布で眠る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:09.97,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}以星空为毯子安眠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.70,0:02:15.21,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}テーブルの向こうの笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.70,0:02:15.21,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}餐桌对面的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:23.65,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}最果ての地を君と目指した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:23.65,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}为你指向尽头之地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:33.16,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}ありがとうはこっちの言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:33.16,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}我才该说谢谢你才对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:51.10,somari title,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,850)\blur6\pos(1540.133,1064.267)}祈祷的相遇和羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:47.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:54.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,这是图书馆的示意图
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,这本珍藏的书好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:07.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,这条路应该是普拉丽娜偷书的时候用的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:10.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,好深啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,是通风用的竖坑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:17.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,目的地的馆长室好像位于最下层
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:19.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:20.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:22.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:27.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,是我不认识的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:30.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,这个声音是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:32.39,somari text,,0,0,0,,有可疑人员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:40.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,有可疑人员  有可疑人员  有可疑人员…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:37.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:41.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,哨兵带上权杖  立刻赶往现场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.11,0:03:47.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,看来好像是给发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:54.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,要跳了  索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:05.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:15.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,深吸一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:37.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:50.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,刚才的声音是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:51.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,不过好像到达目的地了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:02.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:12.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,举起双手趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:14.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,你们进入了禁区
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:16.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,需要接受处罚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:19.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:21.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,是刚才的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:22.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:24.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:27.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,将他们带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,初次见面  旅行者们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:40.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,您就是伊索尔德·内波夫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:44.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  很抱歉我是这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:46.03,somari text,,0,0,0,,吓到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:48.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,没…没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:51.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,我希望你告诉我关于海纳斯传记的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:54.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,为什么要问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:57.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,没关系  蕾格尔司书长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:58.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:03.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,海纳斯传记  真是令人怀念的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:09.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,这说不定也是来自世界母亲的指引吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:11.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.69,0:06:15.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,写了这本书的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:20.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,我将人类逼向了死路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:27.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,我来告诉你们吧  海纳斯传记
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:32.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,我的祖先  菲欧朵拉·内波夫与人类的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:36.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,离魔女的村子还有相当一段距离
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:42.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,这风是老师说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.44,0:07:10.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,你醒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:12.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:16.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,姐姐你倒在了村子外边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:19.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,那个  这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:20.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,海纳斯的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,是这附近最大的村子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:25.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,海纳斯的村子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:28.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,你是哪个村子的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:40.02,somari text,,0,0,0,,你起床了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:52.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,除了脚部的伤外  身体应该没有其他问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:55.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:57.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,你口渴了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:58.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,我去给你取水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:00.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,米娅也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:14.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,是米娅和海纳斯大人找到了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.22,somari text,,0,0,0,,海纳斯大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:19.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,可他看起来和大家不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:22.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,那也是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,海纳斯大人对我们来说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:28.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,是给予了我们住处的神明一样的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,神明？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:34.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,多亏了那位大人我们才能在这里富裕地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:39.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,不过外表和我们不一样  稍微有点吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:44.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,原来如此  也就是和大家是不一样的种族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:48.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:53.01,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是大家也有种族名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:55.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,你是从哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:09:00.22,somari text,,0,0,0,,「种族」是野兽或者植物用的称呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:03.50,somari text,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:08.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,你  不是和我们一样是人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:12.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:14.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,海纳斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:18.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,那个小女孩是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,不用多担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:23.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:26.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,海纳斯大人都说了就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:27.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,不好意思了小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,身体早点好起来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:34.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,这是水  喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:37.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:43.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:47.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,刚才那些人是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:50.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,他们非常畏惧未知的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:52.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,畏惧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:53.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:56.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,我并没有要加害于他们的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:05.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,人类是非常弱小且胆小的种族
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:10.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,直面偏离人类常识生物的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:13.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,只有排除异类才能获得安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:19.01,somari text,,0,0,0,,若是被知道你是其它种族
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:20.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,你也会成为排除的对象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:22.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,那如果我就这样回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:27.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:30.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,你不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:34.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,我会保证你的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:42.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,不好意思  放下心来一不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:47.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,我种族的眼泪有点特别
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:54.50,somari text,,0,0,0,,你真温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:58.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆没有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:02.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,这样啊  你是哥雷姆的种族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:06.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,我是魔女族的菲欧朵拉·内波夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:09.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,我是海纳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:23.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:27.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,给  奶奶说给姐姐你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:29.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:30.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,薯饼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:36.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:37.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.38,0:11:44.39,somari text,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:45.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,这个味道好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:49.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,你也想吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:51.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:53.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,因为薯饼一点都不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:56.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,薯饼虽然很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:59.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是朋友都说蛋糕才可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:02.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,要是吃薯饼就会像老奶奶一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:05.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:10.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,好  完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:14.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:15.50,somari text,,0,0,0,,好厉害好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:18.21,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,这是你帮助我的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:20.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,你是一个特别可爱温柔的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:27.01,somari text,,0,0,0,,我想现在无论是谁看到你吃薯饼的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:30.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,都不会觉得你像老奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:31.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:36.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:38.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,我去给朋友们看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,一定会没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:32.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,看来大家都很熟悉你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:33.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:35.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,脚的情况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,已经没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:37.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:40.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,调查后发现了是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:44.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,周期性出现的龙卷风
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:46.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,绕周围的大海一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:49.01,somari text,,0,0,0,,然后回到原来的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:51.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,如果乘着明早的风的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:53.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,大概就能回到故乡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:58.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:07.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,好不容易才相处得这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:10.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:17.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,姐姐  你明天要回去了是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:19.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.24,0:14:21.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,为什么  一直留在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:25.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:28.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,那就算去了远方也要和我做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:34.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:36.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,我一直是米娅的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:41.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:44.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,是异族
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:46.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,异族出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:02.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么会那样  好残忍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:07.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,求你们不要这样   我什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:10.22,somari text,,0,0,0,,我不是你们的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:13.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,这家伙是什么  竟然还能像人一样说话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:14.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,真是令人作呕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:16.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,赶快让它们闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:26.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,求你们停下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:29.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,不是这样的  明明不是敌人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:32.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,不可以  不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:41.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,你个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:43.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.97,0:15:44.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:45.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,不准再来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:47.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,你们是人类的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:51.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,滚去其他地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:55.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,不能再待在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:58.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,要是被发现了我会被杀死的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:06.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,菲欧朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,在这里待到明早的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,菲欧朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:15.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:17.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,快回答
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:20.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:23.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:27.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,果然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:31.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,快回去吧  大家在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:35.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,我说米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:39.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,如果我是异族你会怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:43.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,姐姐是人类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:47.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,而且我是不会和怪物做朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:52.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:16:59.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:02.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:06.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,菲欧朵拉  你居然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:09.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,米娅  那是米娅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,她受伤了  得赶紧把她救上来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:14.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是要怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,快来人救救米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:22.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,我可以救助米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:24.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:56.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:04.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,你不是人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:06.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,滚出去  怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:08.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,居然欺骗我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.93,0:18:11.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,披着人皮的怪物  令人作呕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:13.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,杀死她  杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:16.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,看在救助米娅的份上就网开一面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:28.50,somari text,,0,0,0,,现在就赶紧离开  异族之人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:31.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:37.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:41.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,别靠近她  那家伙是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:42.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:49.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,姐姐是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:56.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:06.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,海纳斯传记所记述的故事到这里就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:09.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,回到了魔女的村子的菲欧朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:10.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,之后成为了馆长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:14.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,向下一任馆长讲述了这个故事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:17.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,决定千年之内禁止将这个故事写入书中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:25.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,我们认为胆小的人类和我们共同前行还需要时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:29.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,但我却把这一故事写入了书中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:33.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,是我把人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:36.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,那不是馆长你的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:40.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  只不过各种偶然相叠加的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:43.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:45.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,故事里的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:48.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,和索玛丽是同样的人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:52.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,是同样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:56.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽也会像那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:01.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,馆长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:03.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:18.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,好温暖的手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:23.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,你害怕我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:25.91,somari text,,0,0,0,,不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:27.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,我还有很多像你们一样的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:30.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,那么一定没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:33.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,我们一定能够彼此理解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:37.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,就像是菲欧朵拉和米娅之间产生的羁绊一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:39.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:40.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:43.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,绝对不会断裂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:46.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,彼此相爱的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:51.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,相爱的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:53.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:20:58.15,somari text,,0,0,0,,如果要寻找人类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:00.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,就去往尽头之地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:05.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,现在也许他们的子孙还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:07.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:08.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:14.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,我能够在最后遇见你们  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:34.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,愿你们能受到这个世界的庇佑
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,——————ED——————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:23.09,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}並ぶ影の大きさ比べ笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:23.09,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}比较着并排的影子相视而笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:26.66,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}夕暮れを背に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:26.66,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}把夕阳甩在身后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:37.73,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}そっと風に乗せたのは　まだ小さな願い事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:37.73,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}乘风而去的是那小小的祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:44.76,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}永遠とか　生命だとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:44.76,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}什么是永远  什么是生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:49.36,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}何も分からずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:49.36,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}我还一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:23:01.64,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}真っ直ぐな瞳で　見上げた横顔は眩しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:23:01.64,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}只知道当我抬头仰望你时  你的侧脸总是那么地闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:07.99,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}重ねた手に伝う温もりは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:07.99,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}手牵着手传递的这份温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:12.51,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}どんなときも愛をくれたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:12.51,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}无论何时都在给予我爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:18.40,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}溢れ出すこの想いが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:18.40,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}这不断溢出的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:24.17,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}あなたに届く日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:24.17,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}直到传达到给你的那天
